<l>kuṟṟa milaṉāyk kuṭiceytu vāḻvāṉaic </l>
<l>cuṟṟamāc cuṟṟu mulaku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>People will eagerly seek the friendship of the prosperous soul who has raised his family without foul means.</l>
